Cyber Claw:





Cyber Claw took Telitoli's advice, and turned the hallway. She walked along, 
watching her surroundings carefully. She had her teeth bared and her eyes 
wild. Within a few moments, she saw a room with the CR chambers, as the 
Fuzor had promised.

She let out a satisfied noise, gaping her mouth and twitching her tail. She 
entered the room and approached the chamber on the left. She pressed a 
button on the side of it with her foreclaw, then it opened. She looked 
around, then entered. The door closed behind her and she turned her body 
around with her tail going around her side.
